### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "admin@membercare.local",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### Dashboard Summary (replace token)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Members by Branch (replace branch uuid)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/members?branchId={{branchId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Visitor
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/visitors
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branchId": "{{branchId}}",
  "firstName": "Ruth",
  "lastName": "Daniel",
  "phone": "08030003000",
  "firstAttendanceDate": "2026-04-07",
  "firstAttendanceService": "Sunday Worship",
  "invitedBy": "Grace Johnson"
}

### Create Attendance Session
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/attendance/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branchId": "{{branchId}}",
  "sessionTitle": "Midweek Service",
  "sessionType": "Midweek Service",
  "sessionDate": "2026-04-09"
}
